Program: Outlook
Title: Nabeel Yasin
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsbq
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Iraqi poet Nabeel Yasin considers returning home after 25 years in exile. Also, Paul Jones on discovering rare Canadian birds and trees. Education in Malawi. Thomas Dormandy on the history of pain relief. Finally, Palestinian children afraid to leave the house in case they are arrested. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less